OL,3,CProminent Reform UK figure in Wales
OL,4,Csays he supports devolving water sector
OL,6,FA prominent Reform UK figure in Wales
OL,7,Fhas told ITV Wales' Sharp End
OL,8,Fprogramme that he would support
OL,9,Fdevolving the water sector to Wales.
OL,11,FTorfaen County Councillor Jason
OL,12,FO'Connell was one of the first Reform
OL,13,FUK councillors in Wales and continues
OL,14,Fto be a prominent figure in the
OL,15,Fparty's campaigning.
OL,17,FCllr O'Connell's comments come despite
OL,18,Fthe party's only Senedd Member
OL,19,Frecently saying she wouldn't rule out
OL,20,Fscrapping the Senedd altogether if
OL,21,FReform came to power.
