OL,3,CProminent Reform UK figure in Wales
OL,4,Csays he supports devolving water sector
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government announced plans
OL,7,Fon Tuesday to overhaul how water is
OL,8,Fmanaged, regulated, and delivered in
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FOne proposal is the creation of a new,
OL,12,Fdedicated economic regulator for water
OL,13,Fin Wales.
OL,15,FDuring a discussion on Tuesday
OL,16,Fevening's Sharp End programme, Plaid
OL,17,FCymru's Cefin Campbell MS, said: "We
OL,18,Fcan fully devolve water and also sell
OL,19,Fthe water and that is a way we can
OL,20,Fthen bring down bills and invest in
OL,21,Fthe infrastructure."
