OL,4,Csays he supports devolving water sector
OL,6,FWhen asked if he agreed, Reform UK's
OL,7,FCllr Jason O'Connell said: "Yes, I
OL,8,Fwould welcome that... But aside from
OL,9,Fthe financial, and the bills going up,
OL,10,FI think we have to recognise that
OL,11,Fthere is genuine public anger about
OL,12,Fthe state of our waterways in this
OL,13,Fcountry.
OL,15,F"For 26 years it's been left to rumble
OL,16,Fon this way and we've seen Dwr Cymru,
OL,17,Ftheir senior management team, take
OL,18,Fexcessive pay packets for genuinely
OL,19,Fpoor performance."
