OL,3,CProminent Reform UK figure in Wales
OL,4,Csays he supports devolving water sector
OL,6,FReform UK Senedd Member Laura Anne
OL,7,FJones had previously told the BBC that
OL,8,Fshe questioned whether the Welsh
OL,9,FParliament should continue if Reform
OL,10,Fcould not make it "work for Wales".
OL,12,FIn a statement, Leader of the Welsh
OL,13,FConservatives, Darren Millar MS, said:
OL,14,F"We need politicians in Wales who are
OL,15,Ffocused on delivering positive change,
OL,16,Fnot people who want to constantly
OL,17,Ftinker with our constitution.
OL,19,F"Unlike Reform, the Welsh
OL,20,FConservatives are clear. No more
OL,21,Fpowers for the Senedd."
